reviews.title: Pretty bad...
reviews.comment: The gameplay is pretty bad, although it is playable and has a funny concept to it, but there\'s nothing rewarding to play it for. The physics are terrible, and the controls veel stiff and limited. The graphics are bad and the audio is repetitive. Overall the game looks and feels pretty cheap, performance included. I do however think it has a certain charm to it that makes it a bit interesting. As it stands, though, it\'s no more than an OK concept that has potential with a lot of work.
